div.head:
247. Action Memorandum From the Assistant Secretary of State for International
                    Organization Affairs (Maynes) to
                    Secretary of State Vance
                    Source: National Archives, RG 59, Central Foreign Policy File,
                        P780051–0081. Unclassified. Drafted by Roy Haverkamp (IO/AGR), Alberto Mora (IO/AGR), and Morgenthau on February 28;
                        concurred in draft by Holloway;
                            Butcher; Shear; Handwerger; Luzzato;
                            Kriesberg; Boyle; Farrar; and Vernon Johnson. Byrnes initialed for all the officials with the exception of
                        Morgenthau and Mora. Mora also initialed for Haverkamp.
